copy the version specific files, e.g. bond_breakage_measurement/version_specific_functions.*, to base_source 
run the command
make opt3
on the commandline

and an executable will be made in the folder runfile/runfile.run 
also in the folder bond_breakage_measurement/inputfiles you can find an example of a run

see thesis https://dare.uva.nl/search?identifier=d4502bf8-faf8-46ae-851a-c126b461c12e

